summary: Jeff Noble is a commercial photographer who helps everyday people celebrate life.  His keen eye and witty sense of humor work magically together to record individuals of all ages and from all walks of life, doing what they do best. . .just being themselves.His striking images have helped build such notable brands as AT & T, Ford Motor Company, Prudential Life Insurance and The Quaker Oats Company, among others.Jeff is a 1983 graduate of the prestigious Art Center College of Design in Pasadena, California.  He resides in Scottsdale, Arizona, with his wife, Lisa, and their two Dalmatians, Desi and Luci.Specialties: I specialize in the Advertising, Corporate & Editorial Industries
